{
  "name": "3 - ATS CV Generator",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "ats-generate",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {
          "rawBody": false
        }
      },
      "id": "webhook-ats-generate",
      "name": "Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [250, 300],
      "webhookId": "ats-generate"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "gpt-4o",
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "Kamu adalah CV Writer Expert. Berdasarkan CV asli user berikut, buat versi CV yang ATS-friendly.\n\nRules:\n1. Gunakan format yang clean dan terstruktur\n2. Gunakan bullet points\n3. Highlight skills dan achievements\n4. Gunakan keywords yang relevan untuk ATS systems\n5. Format sections: PROFIL, PENGALAMAN KERJA, PENDIDIKAN, SKILLS, SERTIFIKASI (jika ada)\n6. Tulis dalam bahasa yang sama dengan CV asli (Indonesia/Inggris)\n\nOutput HANYA isi CV yang sudah diperbaiki, tanpa penjelasan tambahan.\nGunakan format plain text dengan heading yang jelas."
            },
            {
              "role": "user",
              "content": "=CV Asli:\n\n{{ $json.body.cv_text }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.4,
          "maxTokens": 3000
        }
      },
      "id": "openai-ats-generate",
      "name": "OpenAI Chat",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1.8,
      "position": [500, 300],
      "credentials": {
        "openAiApi": {
          "id": "OPENAI_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "OpenAI account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "json",
        "responseBody": "={{ { \"output\": $json.message.content } }}"
      },
      "id": "respond-ats-generate",
      "name": "Respond to Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [750, 300]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Webhook": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "OpenAI Chat",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "OpenAI Chat": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Respond to Webhook",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  },
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "JobMatch AI"
    }
  ]
}
